# Dissemination of BI Tools, Reports, and Metadata Enhancements

1. New Data Visualization Tool
   - Tableau 2023.2 now available
   - Enhanced geospatial capabilities
   - Improved data preparation features

2. Quarterly Sales Performance Report
   - Published on SharePoint
   - Includes regional breakdowns and YoY comparisons
   - Interactive dashboard for drill-down analysis

3. Customer Segmentation Metadata Update
   - New attributes added: lifetime value and churn risk
   - Retroactively applied to historical data
   - Documentation available in the metadata repository

4. Real-time Inventory Tracking Report
   - Accessible via mobile app
   - Alerts for low stock levels
   - Integrates with supply chain management system

5. Data Quality Metrics Dashboard
   - Weekly updates on data accuracy and completeness
   - Tracks improvement initiatives
   - Available in the BI portal under "Data Governance"

</OUTPUT_TEXT>
